metadata.name: Temari Avocado Tuna #53 #1/8
metadata.description: Relish the enticing Tamari Avocado Tuna sushi NFT, a tantalizing blend for sushi enthusiasts. Encircled by tender slices of avocado and premium tuna, it nestles impeccably seasoned white rice. Embellished with Japanese mayonnaise and morsels of tuna and avocado, this digital sushi radiates culinary finesse. An irresistible and refined creation!
